title: MAUI Hack Day (previously Xamarin)
presenterName: Matt Goldman, Brady Stroud, Jack Pettit, Alec Tucker, Kym Phillpotts, Sam Basu
eventShortDescription:
MAUI Hack Days (previously Xamarin Hack Days) are community-run events for MAUI developers or people who want to learn MAUI for free.

There will be something for everyone. Experienced MAUI developers can share ideas with other experienced developers. If you’re a beginner, then there’s plenty to learn on the day.
